{"content":"    \r\n    <h1 id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView\">\r\n      <span class=\"lang-csharp\">IBindingListView</span>\r\n        Interface\r\n    </h1>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <nav id=\"center-doc-outline\" class=\"doc-outline\" ms.cmpgrp=\"intopic toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"On page navigation\">\r\n      <h3>In this Article</h3>\r\n    </nav><div class=\"summary\">\r\n    \t<p>Extends the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.ibindinglist\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">IBindingList</a> interface by providing advanced sorting and filtering capabilities.</p>\n\r\n    </div><h2>Syntax</h2>\r\n    \r\n    \t<h3>Declaration</h3>\r\n    \t<pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public interface IBindingListView : System.Collections.IList, System.ComponentModel.IBindingList</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n      <h2>Remarks</h2>\r\n      <p>With the IBindingListView interface, you implement advanced sorting as a set of property descriptor-direction pairs. You implement filtering as a string to be interpreted by the data source implementation. The IBindingListView interface is implemented by the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.windows.forms.bindingsource\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">BindingSource</a> class.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <h2>Properties\r\n     summary</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <table class=\"nameValue\">\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_Filter\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">Filter</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Gets or sets the filter to be used to exclude items from the collection of items returned by the data source</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SortDescriptions\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">SortDescriptions</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Gets the collection of sort descriptions currently applied to the data source.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsAdvancedSorting\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">SupportsAdvancedSorting</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Gets a value indicating whether the data source supports advanced sorting.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsFiltering\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">SupportsFiltering</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Gets a value indicating whether the data source supports filtering.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <h2>Methods\r\n     summary</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <table class=\"nameValue\">\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_ApplySort_System_ComponentModel_ListSortDescriptionCollection_\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">ApplySort(ListSortDescriptionCollection)</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Sorts the data source based on the given <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a>.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" enable-platform-filter\">\r\n          <td>\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a href=\"#System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_RemoveFilter\" data-linktype=\"self-bookmark\">RemoveFilter()</a></div>\r\n          </td>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p>Removes the current filter applied to the data source.</p>\n\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </table>\r\n    <section class=\"memberGroup\">\r\n      <header class=\"header enable-platform-filter\" id=\"properties\">\r\n        <h2>Properties\r\n    </h2>\r\n      </header>\r\n    \r\n      <ul class=\"list-clean enable-platform-filter\">\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_Filter\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_Filter_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">Filter</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Gets or sets the filter to be used to exclude items from the collection of items returned by the data source</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public string Filter { get; set; }</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Property Value</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.string\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">String</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>The string used to filter items out in the item collection returned by the data source.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>Your implementation of the Filter property should exhibit the following behavior when the Filter property is set: The data source returns only the items that meet the filter criteria when the list is accessed by item index or when the list is enumerated. The definition of the filter string is dependent on the data-source implementation, but the behavior associated with setting the filter should be modeled on <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.data.datacolumn#System_Data_DataColumn_Expression_\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Expression</a>.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SortDescriptions\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SortDescriptions_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">SortDescriptions</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Gets the collection of sort descriptions currently applied to the data source.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public System.ComponentModel.ListSortDescriptionCollection SortDescriptions { get; }</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Property Value</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p>The <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a> currently applied to the data source.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>The <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a> is a read-only collection, once constructed.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsAdvancedSorting\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsAdvancedSorting_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">SupportsAdvancedSorting</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Gets a value indicating whether the data source supports advanced sorting.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public bool SupportsAdvancedSorting { get; }</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Property Value</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.boolean\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Boolean</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p><code>true</code> if the data source supports advanced sorting; otherwise, <code>false</code>.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>Advanced sorting refers to the ability to sort by multiple columns.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsFiltering\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_SupportsFiltering_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">SupportsFiltering</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Gets a value indicating whether the data source supports filtering.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public bool SupportsFiltering { get; }</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Property Value</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <div class=\"single\">                \r\n                      <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.boolean\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">Boolean</a></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <p><code>true</code> if the data source supports filtering; otherwise, <code>false</code>.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>With the SupportsFiltering property, you implement filtering as a string to be interpreted by the data source implementation.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </section><section class=\"memberGroup\">\r\n      <header class=\"header enable-platform-filter\" id=\"methods\">\r\n        <h2>Methods\r\n    </h2>\r\n      </header>\r\n    \r\n      <ul class=\"list-clean enable-platform-filter\">\r\n    \r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_ApplySort_System_ComponentModel_ListSortDescriptionCollection_\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_ApplySort_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">ApplySort(ListSortDescriptionCollection)</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Sorts the data source based on the given <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a>.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public void ApplySort (System.ComponentModel.ListSortDescriptionCollection sorts);</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n              <h4>Parameters</h4>\r\n              <ul class=\"memberDetails\">\r\n                <li>\r\n                  <dl>\r\n                  <dt>sorts</dt>\r\n                  <dd>\r\n                    <div class=\"lang-csharp\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a></div>\r\n                  </dd>\r\n                  </dl>\r\n                  <p>The <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a> containing the sorts to apply to the data source.</p>\n\r\n                </li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>The <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.listsortdescriptioncollection\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">ListSortDescriptionCollection</a> is a read-only collection, once constructed.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\" enable-platform-filter\" id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_RemoveFilter\">\r\n    \r\n            <a id=\"System_ComponentModel_IBindingListView_RemoveFilter_\"></a>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n          <div class=\"memberName\">\r\n            <div class=\"lang-csharp\">RemoveFilter()</div>        \r\n          </div>\r\n    \r\n            <p>Removes the current filter applied to the data source.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n            <pre class=\"memberDeclaration\"><code class=\"csharp lang-csharp\">public void RemoveFilter ();</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n          \r\n    \r\n            <h4>Remarks</h4>\r\n            <p>With the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"system.componentmodel.ibindinglistview\" data-linktype=\"relative-path\">IBindingListView</a> type, you implement filtering as a string to be interpreted by the data source implementation.</p>\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </section>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n